title: Go Vegan Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Pizza, Raw, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Fusion
description: Vegan restaurant with a salad bar, est. 2015. Offers fresh juices, smoothies, cold pressed coffee, burgers, pancakes, waffles, chia pudding, tofu scrambles, breakfast burritos, omelets. Raw food include wraps, burgers, tostadas, pizza and salads. An on-premises market sells a selection of vegan dry foodstuff, snacks, supplements, personal care items, and books.
